text: Bruneck (; or Burnech) is a comune in South Tyrol in Trentino-Alto Adige/Südtirol, Italy. == Twin towns == Bruneck is twinned with: * Brignoles, France * Groß-Gerau, Germany * Tielt, Belgium * Szamotuły, Poland == References == == Other websites == * Homepage of the municipality Category:Cities in South Tyrol
title: Bruneck
